<br>
PC:<br>
Wasteland and Fallout,<br>
the early Ultima series - even with the crappy graphics they were soooooooo l33t at the time,<br>
Bard's Tale 1 and 2 (Thief of Fate sucked),<br>
Wizardry series - still one of the best computer rpg games imo,<br>
Pirates!<br>
<br>
Console:<br>
Blaster Master - SNES game that had some of the most innovate gameplay for its time (including the first appearance of strafing),<br>
Target Earth - Sega/Master System game that absolutely blew away everything else, however the game never became a &quot;Pac-Man&quot; per se.<br>
<br>
